DocAttribute.Name: SubmittedBy
DocAttribute.Documentation: The identity of the person or organization submitting the cost schedule.

DocAttribute.Name: PreparedBy
DocAttribute.Documentation: The identity of the person or organization preparing the cost schedule.

DocAttribute.Name: SubmittedOn
DocAttribute.Documentation: The date on which the cost schedule was submitted.

DocAttribute.Name: Status
DocAttribute.Documentation: The current status of a cost schedule. Examples of status values that might be used for a cost schedule status include: - PLANNED - APPROVED - AGREED - ISSUED - STARTED

DocAttribute.Name: TargetUsers
DocAttribute.Documentation: The actors for whom the cost schedule was prepared.

DocAttribute.Name: UpdateDate
DocAttribute.Documentation: The date that this cost schedule is updated; this allows tracking the schedule history.

DocAttribute.Name: ID
DocAttribute.Documentation: A unique identification assigned to a cost schedule that enables its differentiation from other cost schedules.

DocAttribute.Name: PredefinedType
DocAttribute.Documentation: Predefined types of cost schedule from which that required may be selected.
